---
import PolicyPage from '../../components/PolicyPage.astro';
import { siteConfig } from '../../data/siteConfig';
import { getTranslation } from '../../i18n/utils';

const locale = 'en';
const title = getTranslation(locale, 'seo.legal.title');
const description = getTranslation(locale, 'seo.legal.description');
const canonicalUrl = '/en/legal-notice';
const updatedAt = '2026-03-09';
---

<PolicyPage
  title={title}
  description={description}
  lang="en"
  canonicalUrl={canonicalUrl}
  pageTitle="Legal notice"
  updatedAt={updatedAt}
>
  <section>
    <h2>1. Website owner</h2>
    <p>This website is owned by Ignacio Amat, a freelance professional providing web design and development services for companies, startups and teams that need stronger digital execution.</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Owner:</strong> Ignacio Amat</li>
      <li><strong>Business activity:</strong> Freelance web design and development</li>
      <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href={`mailto:${siteConfig.email}`}>{siteConfig.email}</a></li>
      <li><strong>Location:</strong> Barcelona, Spain</li>
      <li><strong>Domain:</strong> ignacioamatweb.com</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>2. Purpose of the website</h2>
    <p>This website is intended to present services, selected work, articles, resources and contact options related to the professional activity of its owner.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>3. Terms of use</h2>
    <p>Accessing or browsing this website implies acceptance of these terms of use.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Users must use the website lawfully and in accordance with applicable regulations.</li>
      <li>It is not permitted to use the contents for fraudulent, unlawful or harmful purposes.</li>
      <li>Website availability is not guaranteed at all times, although reasonable effort is made to keep it updated and operational.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>4. Intellectual property</h2>
    <p>The texts, layouts, structure, code, graphic elements and images on this website belong to Ignacio Amat or are used with the relevant permission. Reproduction, distribution or transformation without prior authorization is prohibited except where allowed by law.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>5. Liability</h2>
    <p>The information published on this website is for general informational and commercial purposes and may be updated, changed or removed at any time.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>No liability is accepted for isolated errors, technical interruptions or decisions made solely on the basis of the information contained on the site.</li>
      <li>No responsibility is assumed for the content, operation or policies of third-party websites linked from this website.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>6. External links</h2>
    <p>This website may include links to third-party tools, social networks or websites. Their presence does not imply endorsement or control over their content or legal conditions.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>7. Personal data</h2>
    <p>The processing of personal data is described in the <a href="/en/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>. If you use the contact form or email, your data is only used to manage that communication and any related pre-contractual process.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>8. Governing law</h2>
    <p>This legal notice is governed by Spanish law. Any dispute related to this website shall be submitted to the courts of Barcelona, unless mandatory law provides otherwise.</p>
  </section>
</PolicyPage>
